text:
Ordered
Tom Yum soup : nice!
Basil pork rice : too wet, didn't like it
Garlic pork rice : thought is deep fried pork w garlic bits but it's not.. didn't like it too

Will try other dishes if nearby.

The staff are so nice and friendly! However quite unfortunately Thai basil rice I got wasn't very good, the meat was soggy and not what I expected

I'm sure the other food choices are better tho so maybe get the soups instead of the basil rice
Great tasting authentic Thai food hidden in a kopitiam at reasonable prices. All the food are fresh and tastyâ€¦ Highly recommended the Tom Yum soup. Yummmyyy!!!
Nice, yummy , authentic thai food.. Thai chef. available on panda, grab n deliveroo.. I like the Kai Chiaw ( omelette ) and basil rice.
The tomyum seafood soup is super nice. Fresh prawns and seafood. Price is reasonable. Will definitely back for more other nice Thai food.
